<subSubSection id="B20EA6AF64B150084C6F5B6A5D8368E9" pageId="0" pageNumber="193" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="B4DDF00F546182427351EE96B49D5A3E" pageId="0" pageNumber="193">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="13AC22AFF7ACDF42F74267F1D29E16E6" pageId="0" pageNumber="193">
Verity (1923) proposed this name as a race of 
<taxonomicName id="F15B1418E7CE2996739AF19464BEB9C2" genus="L." lsidName="L. euphemus" pageId="0" pageNumber="193" rank="species" species="euphemus">
<emphasis id="9FB2BE033C502A6DD5202BFCB021CA23" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="193">L. euphemus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="3429B2C3B75323A7D589DE4AE2BC3FF4" originalValue="Hübner">Huebner</normalizedToken>
, 1799-1800. According to 
<bibRefCitation id="2DFE4AB9FEB7FD99AA8F2D56B3CF91C7" author="Kudrna, O" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Research on the Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="193" pagination="1 - 105" refId="B56" refString="Kudrna, O, 1983. An annotated catalogue of the butterflies named by Roger Verity. Journal of Research on the Lepidoptera 21 (1): 1 - 105" title="An annotated catalogue of the butterflies named by Roger Verity." volume="21" year="1983">Kudrna (1983</bibRefCitation>
: 35), this race represents an available subspecific name. However, the year on the specimen labels (1937) indicate specimens were collected 14 years after description (1923) from the same location (i.e., Italy: Bolognola) the original type material was collected. As a result, the black label of the specimens treated as 
<normalizedToken id="FFF39013D18836CB76397412D1A8293B" originalValue="“type”">&quot;type&quot;</normalizedToken>
by Verity is erroneous. The specimen collected from the same geographical location from which the type specimen was collected is called topotype. According to ICZN (1999), a topotype has no formal standing and is not regulated by the Code. Therefore, this specimen is erroneously labelled as type, should be annotated as &quot;Not a Type&quot; and are treated here as 
<normalizedToken id="E0365C2B709592D3A4499FFBDB78AD19" originalValue="“Non-type”">&quot;Non-type&quot;</normalizedToken>
specimen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
